fullContent: Homeâ€º Skibidi ToiletAgent Walker vs Skibidi ToiletsBy OnlineGames.ioMake Game Full ScreenGet ready for funny battles with Skibidi Toilets! Agent Walker vs Skibidi Toilets is a 3D action game where you fight with toilet heads as a four-armed mechanical Agent Walker.You need to eliminate a specific number of Skibidi Toilets to move to the next level. Try your best and clear all the toilet heads running towards you from the battling field in this shooting game!ControlsDesktops and LaptopsLeft Mouse Button: ShootRight Mouse Button: AimMouse: Look AroundWASD or the Arrow Keys: MoveSpacebar: JumpR Key: ReloadV Key: Change Camera ViewTAB: PauseMobile DevicesUse the virtual buttons on the screen to shoot and aimOverview of Agent Walker vs Skibidi ToiletsIn this action game, you are not a regular person trying to defeat the Skibidi Toilets! You will play as a mechanical being with four arms. His name is Agent Walker. And as you can guess, you can have four weapons for four arms.Yes, you have heard right! You have four weapons in your hands. Try to flush all the toilet heads on the playing field in this shooting game. When you manage to clear a specific number of them at each level, you will move to the next one!Four Arms Four WeaponsSince your mechanical Walker has four arms, you can carry four weapons at once. This means that you can also change each of the weapons from the "Weapons" section of the menu. There are six unique arsenals at your disposal. You can find an automatic rifle, a sniper rifle, a minigun, a shotgun, a bazooka and even a katana! Use your earned coins to acquire them.Change Agent Walker's AppearanceIn the beginning, Agent Walker has a regular white camera head. However, as you make progress, you can unlock new kinds of appearances for him. There are various camera heads and other unique looks that you can find in the "Appearance" section. You can even get a satellite view or speaker view for him! Isn't it fantastic?I can't open the game. What should I do?Turn off any ad blockers you are currently using. Alternatively, try launching the game in incognito mode. If these suggestions aren't enough, please see our support page.DeveloperGoGoMan developed the Agent Walker vs Skibidi Toilets.You May Also LikeIf you enjoy playing with Skibidi Toilets, you may also like playing Toilets Attack.
